Class Xbox

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.GenericHID
      • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Joystick
        • com.explodingbacon.bcnlib.utils.Xbox

  • public class Xbox
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Joystick
    An extension class of Joystick that makes it much easier to do Xbox-specific things, such as reading from the DPad or rumbling.
